title: Temple Golem
description: Built of stone, woven with threads of magical filament. It's movements are unexpectedly fluid as it holds a carved sword in salute.

title: Large Rat
description: Bigger than most dogs you've seen, this creature looks at you without a trace of fear.

title: Blooming Vine Wall
description: Covered in vibrant orange flowers and sharp thorns, the vines have woven blockade.

title: Blooming Vine
description: Prehensile vines track your movements menacingly. Glistening thorns are hidden beneath bright orange flower petals.

title: Goblin Darkling
description: A vicious goblin on all fours, glaring. Come from the darkness, feeding on rot.

title: Goblin Hulk
description: A massive goblin creature with thick forearms planted in front of it. It's mouth hangs open, thick saliva shot through with an oily green color cover it's sharp fangs.

title: Giant Centipede
description: Uncountable legs proprel it's articulated body. Light reflects of it's slick chitinous exoskeleton.

title: Grub
description: A crawling maggot the size of a dog wriggled it's way towards you.
